These problems involve graph theory, automata theory, and combinatorics, which are all relevant to the sub-categories of Discrete Mathematics (cs.DM), Computational Complexity (cs.CC), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO), and Computer Science and Game Theory (cs.GT).
